column8: Did he put you up to this...? These family matters are none of your business. But... you can't leave empty-handed, choose a provision. This is not for him, though.
That is... rather generous of you, Your Majesty. Thank you. I would like you to have this as well.
Music is the wish of the soul.
I put my heart in this song.
Feel free to return when you are weary.
I hope this is some small easement.
They just came from the oven.
What can this humbled one do to help?
Your Royal Highness, to what do I owe the pleasure?
As you wish, Your Royal Majesty.
Please do not interrupt my music...
I am in the midst of something.
My work must not be disturbed...
May you find what you seek.
Your Majesty, if it pleases you...
I hope it is to your liking.
